{"tid":14212,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日醫院個邊啲同事差啲比人嚇撚死","createTime":"2016-11-30T11:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T10:57:05.000Z","uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9bc60953f05d68f91a3261962ce77cdf0b5f9c","tid":14212,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:45:28.000Z","msg":"今日原本風平浪靜等收工 諗住唔撚洗搞咁多野 放工返屋企打個靚J瞓教啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知係我臨轉間個一刻就黎料 有條中年呀伯講野一舊舊咁沖入黎大叫 急事呀！讓開呀！急事呀！之後衝左入廁所<br />\n我地當緊值嘅唔知發生咩事緊係攞定晒啲架餐stand by住啦<br />\n幾個同事推緊張病床過黎 鹽水都攞埋過黎 好撚緊急<br />\n正當我地入去廁所之際 個呀伯行左出黎<br />\n我啞撚左咁望住佢 我地成team以為佢有咩急事衝入黎醫院 點解佢依家若無其事咁企係到嘅？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呀伯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呀伯 你無事呀嘛？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 禾可以由咩事？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你頭先講急事喎 你真係無野？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係急事呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩急事？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">急屎呀</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你死老餅 做咁多年人講野都鬼食泥咁 嚇鳩死我地呀 你睇你幾撚無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後由原本6點收工搞撚到7點先收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多得個老野唔少"},{"pid":"672dc3cd2a56e547bf09a2dc9ce21a6d4f44911a","tid":14212,"uid":4391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:18:18.000Z","msg":"你話你係到做乜撚野 你話"},{"pid":"8afa35bb930ee06ba7b34d72eef9c3be7738c7a1","tid":14212,"uid":3558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184fff4f85374f436f7b660ce5ff020ac593aeb4","tid":14212,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3fb865b3f9b8c1d258a9ccac49faed70fb8137","tid":14212,"uid":6057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"睇睇下以為鴻福郎d笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}